Now you can call 050 numbers associated with SkyPhone supported by FC2. Changed some User Interfaces. Now you can save a SkyPhone number in Contacts using a URL scheme skyphone: skyphone number .

Now you can call verified mobile phone numbers associated with SkyPhone supported by FC2. You can call neither landline numbers nor unverified mobile phone numbers. You can make calls with SkyPhone users only.
Improved stability and bug fixes.
Now you can make outgoing calls using a URL scheme skyphone: skyphone number . Stability improvements while calling. Changed some User Interfaces.

SkyPhone numbers have changed from 12 to 8 digits. Added Call quality in the Settings screen and now you can set the sound quality in call as poor high. Added a function to send your SkyPhone number via email in the Profile screen. Now you can switch to the speaker phone while calling. Changed some User Interfaces.
Some user interfaces are changed. The Answer button is now displayed above Memo in 3.5 inch devices including iPhone 4s and so on. Call stability improvements in the low bandwidth mode.
